{"tid":2159343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視點名批評吃播浪費 ，吃播影片下架、直播主帳號即被封","createTime":"2020-08-16T09:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T10:47:44.000Z","uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"400f331df77cb264523de4fc68cffd2cfddc6a96","tid":2159343,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=8470df0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年中國大陸直播風氣興起，各個直播主都各施奇招吸引觀眾眼球，而當中就有一次進食大量食物的吃播出現。央視於 8 月 12 日點名批評「大胃王」、「吃播」等會誤導民眾浪費糧食。而不足 24 小時，網民發現被央視點名的帳號全數消失，從抖音或快手搜尋「大胃王」、「吃播」等字，更會彈出「文明吃播，珍惜糧食」等字樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/photo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fphoto.jpg&h=6e9987bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國官媒央視於 8 月 12 日批評大陸近年流行的「大胃王」及「吃播」風氣是不文明的行為，嚴重誤導民眾浪費糧食，甚至公開點名批評部份「大胃王」直播主。而不足 24 小時，被央視公開點名批評的直播主帳號從社交媒體上全數消失。<br />\n<br />\n今日有網民嘗試在抖音或快手搜尋「大胃王」或「吃播」等字眼，更會彈出「文明吃播，珍惜糧食」等提示字樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/693f-ixreehp1912152.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F693f-ixreehp1912152.jpg&h=94103cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6128-ixreehp1912468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F6128-ixreehp1912468.jpg&h=9e918f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而許多過去人氣頗高的吃播直播主影片被下架。部份直播主回應指，影片下架是為了作出轉型，亦有部份坦言是避免爭議而先行調整。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6d72-ixreehp1911822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F6d72-ixreehp1911822.jpg&h=696349d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一張截圖顯示，有社交平台禁止大胃王吃播等主題，並指違規者將會被封號並不予解封。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/7017-ixreehp1911685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F7017-ixreehp1911685.jpg&h=3cc9b30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n部份大陸網民同意央視說法，並指控部分大胃王直播主是以吃完後催吐的方式嘩眾取寵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/e3d3-ixreehp1911245-543x580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fe3d3-ixreehp1911245-543x580.jpg&h=14fff96a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上有人認為，近日習近平以及央視都高調批評浪費食物，加上中國大陸去年底爆發疫症及最近遭遇嚴重水災，令人聯想到中國或正面臨糧食不足的危機。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源 : 新浪微博"},{"pid":"4866643a0b3fabf146007c1fc62f89da7fd4aeba","tid":2159343,"uid":191467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:21:10.000Z","msg":"睇來真係好唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35eb11fd94a763497283fc389570710807f52a2b","tid":2159343,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"以後轉型直播食草 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D68QH17VUAI-vVX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD68QH17VUAI-vVX.jpg&h=7e0adade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinacn10119/720/w960h560/20191229/3cdb-imkzenp5622907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsinacn10119%2F720%2Fw960h560%2F20191229%2F3cdb-imkzenp5622907.jpg&h=7e05b392&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ddba3c8ec665e99ff0cf30dd762544e7fbbfddc","tid":2159343,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4866643a0b3fabf146007c1fc62f89da7fd4aeba","tid":2159343,"uid":1